    Complex.dot(Complex y, Complex initial, int subtract, int xstep, int ystep, int len, int prec, Complex res)
    Computes the dot product of the vectors x and y, setting res to s+(-1)^subtract+sum(this[i]*y[i],i=0..len-1) The initial term s is optional and can be omitted by passing NULL (equivalently, s=0 ).
